# MyKino Frontend — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env.local for local development.

# ─── AI Proxy (production managed AI) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Point to your server/ instance. Leave empty to use BYO key from Settings.
# VITE_AI_PROXY_URL=http://localhost:3001

# ─── Supabase (cross-device sync) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...     ← Settings → API → anon/public key

# ─── Stripe ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Price IDs are configured server-side in server/.env (STRIPE_PRICE_MONTHLY /
# STRIPE_PRICE_ANNUAL) — never expose them in the frontend build.
